    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Level 4+, Ningyo Clan</p><p>You have developed the Ability to purify any body of water you come across, using your Chakra, and the voice of the Water itself.</p><ul><li>Increase your Charisma or Wisdom by +1</li></ul><p>You can spend 1 Minute to Purify up to 5 Litres of Water. Creatures who drink this Water regain hit point as if they rolled X Hit die (X = Your Proficiency Bonus), and may end any one elemental or physical condition on themselves. They must consume at least 500ml of this water to gain this effect, and may only do so twice long per rest. You may use this feature once per long rest.</p>",
